=== 製作與開發 ===
2015年1月18日，[[FX_(電視頻道)|FX]]宣布預訂由[[潘蜜拉·艾德隆|潘蜜拉·艾德隆]]與[[路易·C·K|路易·C·K]]共同開創，艾德隆主演、路易·C·K執導之新喜劇試播集。<ref name="Pilot Order">{{cite web|last1=Andreeva|first1=Nellie|title=FX Orders Comedy Pilot Starring Pamela Adlon From Louis CK|url=http://deadline.com/2015/01/pamela-adlon-louis-ck-comedy-pilot-fx-1201352796/|publisher=Deadline.com|accessdate=2015-08-13|date=2015-01-18|archive-date=2015-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150727031739/http://deadline.com/2015/01/pamela-adlon-louis-ck-comedy-pilot-fx-1201352796/|dead-url=no}}</ref>艾德隆與路易·C·K也將和布萊爾·布雷德（{{lang|en|Blair Breard}}）及{{le|戴夫·貝奇|Dave Becky}}共同擔任執行製作，並由{{link-en|3藝術娛樂|3 Arts Entertainment}}與[[FX_(電視頻道)|FX製作公司]]共同製作。<ref name="Pilot Order"/>本劇可算是基於潘蜜拉·艾德隆個人生活改編的半自傳影集。<ref name=deadline1201495143>{{cite web|last1=Andreeva|first1=Nellie|title=Louis C.K.-Pamela Adlon Comedy ‘'Better Things'’ Gets FX Series Order|url=http://deadline.com/2015/08/better-things-louis-ck-pamela-adlon-fx-comedy-series-1201495143/|publisher=Deadline.com|accessdate=2015-08-13|date=2015-08-07|archive-date=2015-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150811085855/http://deadline.com/2015/08/better-things-louis-ck-pamela-adlon-fx-comedy-series-1201495143/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年8月7日，FX正式宣布預訂系列10集集數。<ref name=thr>{{cite web|last1=Rose|first1=Lacey|title=Louis C.K., Pamela Adlon's ''Better Things'' Comedy Lands Series Order at FX|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/louis-ck-pamela-adlons-fx-813831|website=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|accessdate=2015-08-13|date=2015-08-07|archive-date=2015-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150809235822/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/louis-ck-pamela-adlons-fx-813831|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Littleton|first1=Cynthia|title=FX Networks Gives Series Orders to Comedies ''Better Things'', ''Cassius and Clay''|url=http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/fx-better-things-louis-c-k-cassius-and-clay-1201559052/|website=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]|accessdate=2015-08-13|date=2015-08-07|archive-date=2015-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150809223326/http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/fx-better-things-louis-c-k-cassius-and-clay-1201559052/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

本劇劇名取自[[奇想樂團|奇想樂團]]的歌曲〈{{link-en|更美好的事 (歌曲)|Better Things (song)|更美好的事}}〉。<ref name=Vulture-BetterThings-2016>{{cite news|last1=Fernandez|first1=Maria Elena|title=Pamela Adlon Can't Believe She Has Her Own Show|url=http://www.vulture.com/2016/09/pamela-adlon-better-things-conversation.html|accessdate=2016-09-12|work=[[紐約_(雜誌)|Vulture]]|date=2016-09-08|archive-date=2016-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911004433/http://www.vulture.com/2016/09/pamela-adlon-better-things-conversation.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年9月20日，FX宣布續訂第2季。<ref name="Season2 Renewed">{{cite web |url=http://tvline.com/2016/09/20/atlanta-renewed-better-things-season-2-fx/ |title=Atlanta, Better Things Renewed at FX |publisher={{link-en|TVLine|TVLine}} |first=Andy |last=Swift |date=2016-09-20 |accessdate=2016-09-20 |archive-date=2019-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401155556/https://tvline.com/2016/09/20/atlanta-renewed-better-things-season-2-fx/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年10月19日，FX宣布續訂第3季。<ref name="Season 3 Renewed">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/10/better-things-renewed-season-3-fx-1202191273/|title=‘Better Things’ Renewed For Season 3 By FX|publisher=Deadline.com|author=Denise Petski|date=2017-10-19|accessdate=2017-10-19|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019204427/http://deadline.com/2017/10/better-things-renewed-season-3-fx-1202191273/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年11月10日，由於路易·C·K爆發對多名女性性騷擾的醜聞，在經本人證實與公開致歉後，FX正式終止與他及其製作公司Pig Newton的合作，他也將不再製作本劇，並從執行製作中除名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/11/fx-cuts-ties-louis-c-k-ends-pig-newton-1202206037/|title=FX Cuts Ties With Louis C.K., Ends Overall Deal With His Pig Newton Company|publisher=Deadline.com|author=Erik Pedersen|date=2017-11-10|accessdate=2017-11-10|archive-date=2017-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171111022424/http://deadline.com/2017/11/fx-cuts-ties-louis-c-k-ends-pig-newton-1202206037/|dead-url=no}}</ref>對此，身為長期夥伴與朋友的艾德隆在震驚及痛心之餘，亦對遭遇不幸的女性感到悲痛與同情。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/11/pamela-adlon-louis-c-k-devastated-and-in-shock-after-his-admission-of-misconduct-1202206147/|title=Pamela Adlon On Louis C.K.: “Devastated” After His “Admission Of Abhorrent Behavior”|publisher=Deadline.com|author=Erik Pedersen|date=2017-11-10|accessdate=2017-11-10|archive-date=2017-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171111052300/http://deadline.com/2017/11/pamela-adlon-louis-c-k-devastated-and-in-shock-after-his-admission-of-misconduct-1202206147/|dead-url=no}}</ref>11月13日，艾德隆開除了對路易·C·K惡行知情卻隱瞞、長期擔任她經紀人的3藝術娛樂製作人貝奇。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/11/pamela-adlon-drops-manager-dave-beck-louis-c-k-sexual-misconduct-scandal-1202207277/|title=Pamela Adlon Drops Manager Dave Becky Amid Louis C.K. Sexual Misconduct Scandal|publisher=Deadline.com|author=Nellie Andreeva|date=2017-11-13|accessdate=2018-04-21|archive-date=2018-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180420220851/https://deadline.com/2017/11/pamela-adlon-drops-manager-dave-beck-louis-c-k-sexual-misconduct-scandal-1202207277/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年1月5日，FX主席{{le|約翰·蘭卓拉夫|John Landgraf}}於冬季[[電視評論家協會|電視評論家協會]]上，表示雖然調查結果顯示路易·C·K在與電視網合作的這8年中，並未有偏差行為，但他仍不會回歸本劇製作陣容，「這是潘蜜拉的節目，這是她的故事、她的人生。路易只是她的寫作夥伴，而她將獨自撰寫（集數）或尋覓其他作家共同執筆。她是節目的形象、創作的泉源。他（路易）在未來不會參與FX的任何節目，包括《更美好的事》。我對潘蜜拉相當有信心。」他說道。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2018/01/louis-ck-sexual-harrasment-john-landgraf-fx-investigation-1202236370/|title=Louis C.K. Sexual Harassment Investigation; Comedian’s Involvement On ‘Better Things’ – TCA|publisher=Deadline.com|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|date=2018-01-05|accessdate=2018-01-05|archive-date=2018-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180105212423/http://deadline.com/2018/01/louis-ck-sexual-harrasment-john-landgraf-fx-investigation-1202236370/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

艾德隆認為本劇描繪的家庭情節，是觀眾產生共感的原因之一，而各人的成長經驗也使他們能與節目相連結，因此本劇並不只是為了母親或女兒的身分而生。不希望劇集定位為「美國主題節目」的艾德隆，試圖讓國際觀眾也能產生共鳴，並確立當觀眾不再有與劇集連結的感受時，便是故事的終點。艾德隆稱執導第2季全季集數的心情是振奮多於疲憊，也證實第3季會加入新編劇，並於2018年2月展開製作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2018/scene/news/pamela-adlon-better-things-universally-relatable-1202770240/|title=Pamela Adlon: When ‘Better Things’ ‘Stops Being Relatable Is When I Stop Doing My Show’|publisher=綜藝雜誌|author=Ariana Brockington|date=2018-04-20|accessdate=2018-04-20|archive-date=2018-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421035347/http://variety.com/2018/scene/news/pamela-adlon-better-things-universally-relatable-1202770240/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

